org.kite.services

Class CommandService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • org.kite.services.CommandService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Executor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WiredService

    public abstract class CommandService
extends Service
implements java.util.concurrent.Executor
    A helpful android.app.Service extension, that can execute commands in separate Executor. In conjunction with AsyncMethod can be used to enqueue work in background.
    See Also:
    MainThreadExecutor, WiredService
